subject: Baseball
Playoff Games
lead_paragraph: Cole Hamels pitched a three-hitter, Adrian Beltre hit a go-ahead homer and the Rangers beat the visiting Angels, 9-2, on Sunday, eliminating Los Angeles from playoff contention.
